			<br />Units:<br />Unemployment Rate: Percent, Magnitude = Units<br /><br /><a id="footnotes"><b>Footnotes:</b></a><br />On 1 November 2010, the new Auckland territorial authority (TA) replaced the existing: Rodney District, North Shore City, Auckland City, Waitakere City, Manukau City, Papakura District, and part of Franklin District councils.<br />The changes were introduced in the release for the June 2011 quarter and backcast for the March 2011 quarter.<br />This has resulted in minor changes in the boundary between the Auckland and Waikato regions. The new boundaries do not significantly affect measures from the Household Labour Force Survey (HLFS).<br /> <br />Symbols:<br />.. figure not available<br />C: Confidential<br />E: Early Estimate<br />P: Provisional<br />R: Revised<br />S: Suppressed<br /><br />Status flags are not displayed<br /><br />Table reference: <br />HLF051AA<br /><br />Last updated:<br />Unemployment Rate: 04 February 2026 10:45am<br /><br />Source: Statistics New Zealand<br />Contact: Information Centre<br />Telephone: 0508 525 525<br />Email:<a href="mailto:info@stats.govt.nz">info@stats.govt.nz</a><br /><br /><br /></td>
